name: NYX COSMETICS WORTH THE HYPE MASCARA – BLACK
description: It’s all in the name really, NYX Professional Makeup Worth The Hype Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara is your jam for long, full eyelashes that last from the office to cocktails. A breeze to apply, and comfortable to wear, this volumizing mascara features a tapered brush tip coating every lash (even the baby ones on the bottom!) in buildable, lengthening color.
